    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR6q0092-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a03.s1" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-06T16:13:44.357+09:00">Preface</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a05.s1" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-06T16:14:23.655+09:00">Yang Jie, Senior Gentleman for Court Audiences, Minister, Vice Director of theMinistry of Personnel, and Military Protector</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a0701.s1" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-06T16:16:15.063+09:00">When the Buddhas proclaim the truth,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a0701.s2" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-06T16:16:19.718+09:00">they consider mind as zong [i.e., the implicit truth].</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a0701.s3" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-06T16:16:34.604+09:00">When sentient beings express their faith</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a0701.s4" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-06T16:16:45.395+09:00">they consider zong as a mirror.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a0701.s5" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-06T16:17:07.98+09:00">The world of sentient beings is the world of the Buddhas [i.e., there is no difference between them].</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a0701.s6" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-06T16:17:15.704+09:00">It is because of their delusion that they become sentient beings.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a0701.s7" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-06T16:17:31.385+09:00">The mind of the Buddhas is the mind of sentient beings.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a0701.s8" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-06T16:17:34.765+09:00">It is because of their realization that they become Buddhas.</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
